pkgmetadata.longdescription: Saghatelian et al. (2004) FAAH knockout LC/MS data // Positive ionization mode data in NetCDF file format. Centroided subset from 200-600 m/z and 2500-4500 seconds. Data originally reported in "Assignment of Endogenous Substrates to Enzymes by Global Metabolite Profiling" Biochemistry; 2004; 43(45). Also includes detected peaks in an xcmsSet.
